{"tid":2292771,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"番左工之後唔想再浪費咁多時間去維繫友誼","createTime":"2020-11-19T18:04:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T16:59:52.000Z","uid":59471,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c538f6a6b657f9a2974c1a3b068c0fb02b35c605","tid":2292771,"uid":59471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T18:04:32.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n以前未返工嗰陣時，會成日同friend食飯出街，就算每日出都可以⋯<br />\n但係返咗工之後，只係會想同最熟相處最舒服既朋友岀去，可能返工個時用得太多精神同同事social，係最私人嘅時間嗰陣時只係想做返自己⋯<br />\n慢慢好似同好多朋友疏遠咗咁，就算嗌咗交都完全無力去tum，夜深人靜嗰陣時會覺得有少少可惜，不過事後都係無理到，有無人都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n返工真係好撚累呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c8ff2871db5ad22f7e7657ae968f8274cb384c2","tid":2292771,"uid":324265,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T18:06:44.000Z","msg":"社交技能差劣 建議考牌"},{"pid":"8227b20eca05376d736c5be85ea33e58d5c5948d","tid":2292771,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T18:09:37.000Z","msg":"放工龜屋企<br />\n返到去又要幫手做家務<br />\n食飯睇下電視都10半<br />\n沖涼吹頭上網又12半<br />\n邊撚到仲有時間?<br />\n最多六日會約打波睇戲食飯"},{"pid":"ce161bdacff50f654918073458037eaad6231abe","tid":2292771,"uid":353819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T16:31:37.000Z","msg":"Agger 懶理社交禮儀<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1211f466116d3acbc8db63036e0e557cb05127e8","tid":2292771,"uid":9392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T16:59:52.000Z","msg":"全部係過客"}]}